        alt="Burger squad"
        style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);"
      />
      <p style="margin-top: 1.2rem; text-align: left; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.9;">
        Do you remember that dream? Where we buy out a row of brownstones? We promised to have more wine and movie nights, AYCE raids, karaoke, bakeoffs, and that our dogs would be friends.
      </p> -->
